text: Bent Høie (born 4 May 1971) is a Norwegian politician from the Conservative Party who is the county governor of Rogaland since 2021. He previously was the Minister of Health and Care Services from 2013 to 2021, and a member of the Storting from Rogaland from 2000 to 2021.
